        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer40785873" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer11759046520731937759">This is a very well done book. If you have any interest in learning about transgender youth culture, and/or transgender teens of color, or being a youth of color this is very informative. There are many issues at intersection here, youth rights, poverty, tension between generations in immigrant culture, drugs, queerness, beauty, gender, education etc. Written by a queer woman who taught, advocated for, and be-freinded several poor, trans-gender teens of color living in group homes or on the stre</span>
  <span id="freeText11759046520731937759" style="display:none">This is a very well done book. If you have any interest in learning about transgender youth culture, and/or transgender teens of color, or being a youth of color this is very informative. There are many issues at intersection here, youth rights, poverty, tension between generations in immigrant culture, drugs, queerness, beauty, gender, education etc. Written by a queer woman who taught, advocated for, and be-freinded several poor, trans-gender teens of color living in group homes or on the streets in Los Angeles. </span>
  <a data-text-id="11759046520731937759" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

