        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer24255170" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer6423818058570528011">this book was fucking amazing. cris beam manages to let the natural humor of her subjects flow through without making fun of them! which is quite a fine line. this book is moving, sad, fascinating and touching, and one of the rare books about transpeople i&apos;ve read that shows them as full people, not just as their trangendered identity. there&apos;s plenty of facts, too, if you&apos;re into those, and i learned a lot. yay!</span>
  <span id="freeText6423818058570528011" style="display:none">this book was fucking amazing. cris beam manages to let the natural humor of her subjects flow through without making fun of them! which is quite a fine line. this book is moving, sad, fascinating and touching, and one of the rare books about transpeople i've read that shows them as full people, not just as their trangendered identity. there's plenty of facts, too, if you're into those, and i learned a lot. yay!</span>
