<div class='bookAuthorProfile__about'>

<span id="freeTextContainer1375087185647862347">Cris Beam is a journalist who has written for several national magazines as well as for public radio. She has an MFA in nonfiction from Columbia University and teaches creative writing at Columbia and the New School. She lives in New York.</span>

